# AuroraForge – Code Owners
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global fallback — platform team reviews everything
*                                         @your-org/platform-team

# Domain core — principal engineer sign-off required
services/auroraforge-core/               @your-org/principal-engineers

# Security-sensitive modules
services/auroraforge-auth/               @your-org/security-team @your-org/platform-team
services/auroraforge-keymgmt/            @your-org/security-team @your-org/platform-team

# Infrastructure as Code
infrastructure/                          @your-org/infra-team
k8s/                                     @your-org/infra-team
.github/                                 @your-org/platform-team

# CI pipeline changes
.github/workflows/                       @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team

# Avro schemas — schema evolution must be reviewed carefully
services/auroraforge-avro/               @your-org/data-platform-team @your-org/principal-engineers
